<h1 style="background-color:powderblue;">Hope For The Displaced</h1>
<p style="background-color:powderblue;">Less Fortunate Does Not Mean Less Capable!</p>

<img src="counseling.webp" width="400" height="200">
<h2 style="background-color:powderblue;">Goals of our program.</h1>
<p>Provide career mentoring</p>
<p>Provide a safe place to rest, heal and grow</p>
<p>Support the participant with finding a career</p>
<p>Support the participant in opening and maintaining a savings and checking account</p>
<p>Support the participant in finding and maintaining housing</p>
<p>Assisting the participant in getting insured and finding both physical and mental healthcare</p>

<img src="volunteer.webp" width="200" height="200">
<h3 style="background-color:powderblue;">Benefits of our program.</h3>
<p>Spa and Styling services</p>
<p>Resume building assistance</p>
<p>Transportation to interviews and work</p>
<p>Childcare during participant's working hours</p>
<p>Career Counseling</p>
<p>Insurance and Healthcare Assistance</p>
<p>Housing Assistance</p>
<p>Parenting Classes</p>

<img src="success.webp" width="400" height="200">
<h4 style="background-color:powderblue;">What happens after?</h4>
<p>12 monthly accountability check ins</p>
<p>12 months of financial counseling</p>
<p>Transfer to state assisted child care</p>
<p>Set the participant up with reliable transportation</p>

<h5 style="background-color:powderblue;">You Can Find Additional Assistance Below!</h5>
<p><a href="https://oklahoma.gov/ohca/individuals/mysoonercare/apply-for-soonercare-online/where-to-apply.html">SoonerCare Application</a>
<p><a href="https://www.opencounseling.com/oklahoma/tulsa">Free and Sliding Scale Health Services</a>



